BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-21T03:30:00&endDate=2026-06-22T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nELIZABETH LINE: Sunday 21 June\, no service between Paddington and Abbey Wood / Stratford. Trains operate between Paddington National Rail Station and Heathrow / Reading\, and between Liverpool Street National Rail Station and Gidea Park / Shenfield.
DTEND:20260622T002900Z
DTSTART:20260621T033000Z
SUMMARY:Elizabeth line: Part Closure
UID:83d424fc-f301-4c60-bc12-21f38b478527@83d4.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-29T21:00:00&endDate=2026-06-30T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nELIZABETH LINE: Monday 29 June\, Tuesday 30 and Wednesday 1 July\, after 2200 each evening\, a reduced service operates between Paddington and Heathrow Terminal 4 / Maidenhead. Two trains an hour serve Heathrow Terminal 4\, West Drayton\, Langley\, Slough\, Burnham and Maidenhead. Four trains an hour serve Heathrow Terminals 2 and 3. Six trains an hour serve Ealing Broadway\, Southall and Hayes & Harlington. After 2300\, trains will not call at Acton Main Line\, West Ealing and Hanwell.
DTEND:20260630T002900Z
DTSTART:20260629T210000Z
SUMMARY:Elizabeth line: Reduced Service
UID:002b4401-e6e5-4c8d-a9c4-4cf71c29bb91@002b.org
END:VEVENT
